129
00:09:18,000 --> 00:09:20,000
 jest

130
00:09:20,000 --> 00:09:22,000
 da znaš iskočiti iz

131
00:09:22,000 --> 00:09:24,000
 nekog ustaljenoga

132
00:09:24,000 --> 00:09:26,000
 svog konfora

133
00:09:26,000 --> 00:09:30,000
 jer ako to u životu ne bi bilo tako

134
00:09:30,000 --> 00:09:32,000
 da nekad trebamo i riskirati

135
00:09:32,000 --> 00:09:34,000
 nekad nešto promijenti

136
00:09:34,000 --> 00:09:38,000
 danas ja gledam i ove mlade puno problema imaju

137
00:09:38,000 --> 00:09:40,000
 naravno sve ih razumijem

138
00:09:40,000 --> 00:09:44,000
 ali lakše je biti u konforu obiteljskog doma

139
00:09:44,000 --> 00:09:46,000
 ne iskočiti iz okvira

140
00:09:46,000 --> 00:09:48,000
 preuzeti odgovornost odseliti od kuće

141
00:09:48,000 --> 00:09:50,000
 naći posao lakše je u konforu

142
00:09:50,000 --> 00:09:52,000
 ako se neko brine za mene

143
00:09:52,000 --> 00:09:53,000
 pa treba riskirati

144
00:09:53,000 --> 00:09:54,000
